WEBVTT

00:03:59.807 --> 00:04:01.627
and asked to make their picture.

00:04:02.478 --> 00:04:05.592
Most women cried when I photographed them.

00:04:05.592 --> 00:04:07.768
On the first day,
my fixer, Emine, and I cried

00:04:07.768 --> 00:04:10.971
with almost every woman
who visited our studio.

00:04:12.876 --> 00:04:15.882
There had been such a noticeable
absence of women

00:04:15.882 --> 00:04:17.625
up until that point.

00:04:17.625 --> 00:04:19.918
And the color of their pastel coats,

00:04:19.918 --> 00:04:21.656
their shiny handbags,

00:04:21.656 --> 00:04:23.746
and the bunches of red carnations,

00:04:23.746 --> 00:04:26.952
white tulips and yellow roses
that they carried

00:04:26.977 --> 00:04:29.113
jarred with the blackened square

00:04:29.113 --> 00:04:31.419
and the blackened men
who were encamped there.